      <section eId="sec_7_1_312">
        <num>7-1-312</num>
        <content>
          <p>A trust company which is not a bank may, apart from its fiduciary activities, invest in stock and investment securities, except that it may not acquire or hold its own stock otherwise than pursuant to paragraphs (8) and (9) of Code Section 7-1-261.</p>
          <p>(Code 1933, ยง 41A-1403, enacted by Ga. L. 1974, p. 705, ยง 1.)</p>
